moveNode

  • moveNode(target, destination, emitUpdate?, updatePropagationFct?, cmdMetadata?): {
        root: DataNode;
        update: Updates<DataNode>;
    }

  • Parameters

    • target: string | DataNode

      the node to move

    • destination: {
          direction?: "above" | "below";
          reference: string | DataNode;
      }
      • Optionaldirection?: "above" | "below"
        • if 'above': put the node above the reference
          • if 'below'; put the node below the reference
          • if 'none': add the node as child of reference
      • reference: string | DataNode

        a node used as reference

    • emitUpdate: boolean = true

      whether or not to notify the update

    • updatePropagationFct: UpdatePropagationFct<DataNode> = ...

      a function that is called to append properties on node

    • cmdMetadata: unknown = undefined

      metadata to add to the command

    Returns {

        update: Updates<DataNode>;
    }
